# Card styling: no border radius

All card components in this project use **sharp corners** (no border radius).

## Rule

- When adding or editing **card**-like components (e.g. `.card`, `.reviewCard`, `.columnCard`, `.blogParallaxCard`, `.relatedPostCard`, `.articleCard`, `.serviceCard`, `.categoryCard`, `.reasonCard`, `.staffAreaCard`, `.relatedCard`, and any new card containers), set:
  - `border-radius: 0;`
- Do **not** use `border-radius: var(--radius-md)`, `var(--radius-sm)`, or any pixel value for card containers.

## Example

```css
/* ✅ Correct */
.myCard {
  background: var(--bg-white);
  border-radius: 0;
  box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
}

/* ❌ Avoid for cards */
.myCard {
  border-radius: 8px;
  border-radius: var(--radius-md);
}
```

This applies to any new card components created from now on.
